item.description:
@dain_bramage wrote:

The maps are not included in the cache, rather they were sent to the client when they were requested (when the player was loading a new region). You can attempt to dump the 317 maps and use them (assuming you have the ability to remove objects that weren’t in the 194 revision), but it’s not worth the effort.
TL;DR: No 194 maps.
